OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FRabbi Mendy Singer says Bristol's
OL,7,FJewish community are suffering as
OL,8,Freported antisemitic hate crimes in
OL,9,Fthe South West double in a year.
OL,11,FThere were 50 incidents of
OL,12,Fantisemitism in the Avon and Somerset
OL,13,Fforce area between 2024 to 2025 but
OL,14,Fthis number jumped to 96 in the year
OL,15,Fto April.
OL,17,FThere were 77 reported antisemitic
OL,18,Fhate crimes in 2025, 46 in 2024 and 56
OL,19,Fin 2023, according to data released by
OL,20,Fthe local police.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
