OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FAmid the recent surge in antisemitic
OL,7,Fattacks in the capital, he says the
OL,8,Flocal community are cancelling events,
OL,9,Ffear for their security and live in
OL,10,Fconstant trepidation about threats in
OL,11,Fthe street.
OL,13,FThere are around 10,000 Jews who live
OL,14,Fin the South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
