OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778587868
OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FRabbi Singer, from the Chabad of
OL,7,FBristol, told ITV West Country he
OL,8,Fregularly hears from members of the
OL,9,FJewish community that they feel afraid
OL,10,Fof going out wearing identifiable
OL,11,Fsymbols of their religion, such as a
OL,12,FKippah or Star of David necklace.
OL,14,FHe continued: "People are afraid to
OL,15,Fcome to synagogues given recent
OL,16,Fattacks across the country and
OL,17,Fsynagogues are needing security.
OL,19,F"We're having to reconsider what
OL,20,Fpractical physical measures can be
OL,21,Fimplemented to reassure people."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
