CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778587868
OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FHe believes the hostility towards the
OL,7,FJewish community has only been
OL,8,F"exacerbated" since the October 7
OL,9,Fattacks, when Hamas targeted young
OL,10,FIsraelis at a music festival in 2023,
OL,11,Fand says it has left many Jews in the
OL,12,FSouth West considering leaving England.
OL,14,FRabbi Singer said: "Antisemitism is an
OL,15,Fearly warning sign of what happens in
OL,16,Fsociety - looking back at history,
OL,17,FJews are usually the first group to be
OL,18,Fattacked.
OL,20,F"This should be a wake-up call for
OL,21,Fauthorities to address it seriously".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
