OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778587868
OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FHe said local Jewish businesses have
OL,7,Ffaced threats and had businesses
OL,8,Faffected.
OL,10,FClare Moody, Police and Crime
OL,11,FCommissioner for Avon and Somerset
OL,12,FPolice, said the increase in hate
OL,13,Fcrimes against Jewish communities "has
OL,14,Fa real consequence" on people's lives.
OL,16,FShe added: "There is no excuse for
OL,17,Fantisemitic crime".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
