PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778587868
OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FMs Moody also explained that "state-
OL,7,Fbacked promotion of antisemitism" amid
OL,8,Fthe conflict in the Middle East is
OL,9,Fsomething the national government are
OL,10,Ftaking "very seriously".
OL,12,F"Iran as a state is looking to promote
OL,13,Fharm in our communities and that's
OL,14,Funderlying antisemitism".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
