PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778587868
OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FMs Moody urged more people to report
OL,7,Fif they feel they have been a victim
OL,8,Fof a hate crime, and added that the
OL,9,Flocal force are keeping close contact
OL,10,Fwith Jewish communities and have
OL,11,Fimplemented extra patrols outside
OL,12,FBristol's two synagogues.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Rabbi Singer believes local
OL,15,Fpolice are doing their best to support
OL,16,Fthe community but are "limited in what
OL,17,Fthey can do".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
