OL,3,CRabbi says Jewish communities live in
OL,4,Cfear as antisemitic hate crimes double
OL,6,FHe says the power "ultimately remains
OL,7,Fwith local authorities" and the
OL,8,Fgovernment to consider what greater
OL,9,Fsteps should be taken.
OL,11,F"This is where the the community feels
OL,12,Fshort-changed - not enough
OL,13,Fresponsibilities are being taken by
OL,14,Fhigher authorities."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
